title: Rangoon Dialogue Promo | Saif Ali Khan Confesses His Love For Julia Aka Kangana - Koimoi
text: Here’s the brand new dialogue promo of Rangoon featuring Saif Ali Khan and Kangana Ranaut. The film is a period drama set in the background of World War 2. It also stars Shahid Kapoor in a key role. The promo features, Saif’s character confessing his love for Kangana’s character Julia. Check out the dialogue promo: Directed by Vishal Bharadwaj, the film is slated to release on 24th February,2016. SHARE
